  "description": "Maqam 0 — chromatic, all twelve tones available. Without a modal center, GENDY's random walk has no gravitational attractor: gravity set low (0.3), barrier elasticity high (0.9). The particles bounce between their barriers and ricochet back with full energy. Notes arrive without resolution, drift without purpose, beautiful precisely because they promise nothing. A prophecy in a language with no grammar.",
